---
import Icon from "./ui/Icon/Icon.astro";
---

<section class="box skills">
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon
      icon="terminal-window"
      color="var(--accent-regular)"
      size="2.5rem"
      gradient
    />
    <h2>AI & Data Science</h2>
    <p>
      I build practical projects in NLP and computer vision.
      For Turkish tweets, I experimented with sentiment analysis
      and text classification by fine-tuning VRLLab/TurkishBERTweet
      on small datasets. I also have experience with YOLOv8 for object
      detection and SORT for tracking.
    </p>
    <p>
      In agriculture projects, I worked on fruit ripeness detection using
      hyperspectral images applying PCA and CARS for dimensionality 
      reduction and band selection, testing AlexNet, Random Forest, and 
      Decision Tree. Another project focused on predicting estrus in cows 
      using behavioral and physiological indicators, creating simple prototypes.
  </p>
  </div>
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon icon="code" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
    <h2>Data Engineering & Analysis</h2>
    <p>
      I set up Python-based data workflows: Selenium tweet scraping, cleaning,
      labeling, and analysis. I regularly use Pandas and NumPy for EDA, feature 
      selection, and simple dimensionality reduction. The goal is to prepare data
      cleanly, understandably, and reproducibly before feeding it into models.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon
      icon="rocket-launch"
      color="var(--accent-regular)"
      size="2.5rem"
      gradient
    />
    <h2>Machine Learning Projects</h2>
    <p>
       I applied deep learning (YOLOv8, AlexNet) and classic ML methods to projects 
       including social media sentiment analysis, hyperspectral fruit ripeness detection, 
       estrus detection in cows, and video object tracking. My focus is on <em>working and 
       understandable prototypes</em> rather than production-scale claims.
  </p>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .box {
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .skills {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .skills h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  .skills p {
    color: var(--gray-300);
    max-width: 35rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 60em) {
    .box {
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .skills {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5rem;
    }

    .skills h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }
  }
</style>
